data.description: You will love the expansive living space to be found in this almost new 5 bedroom/3 bath Capri floor plan with upgrades around every corner.  This beautiful home offers a covered entryway with a glass inset front door opening to the spacious living area with a desirable neutral color palette featuring luxury vinyl plank flooring, high ceilings, and recessed lighting.  Stunningly equipped chef's kitchen with upgraded energy-efficient appliances, granite countertops, a large island with bar-height seating for casual dining, and a pantry for all of your storage needs. The owner's suite comes equipped with an oversized walk-in closet and an en suite bath with a double-sink vanity and luxurious step-in shower.  Fantastic extras to appreciate include four guest bedrooms, an inside laundry room, vinyl privacy fencing, a shed for extra storage space, and a screened-in Florida room ready for relaxing or outdoor entertaining.  This home is located in the Marion Oaks community offering a community center, playground, tennis courts, workout facility, library, grocery & other local businesses with no HOA fees. This community is also conveniently located a short distance from the Rainbow River for tubing, kayaking, and boating and only 30 minutes from the World Equestrian Center.
